(54052, 'esMX', 'Questfall', 'Slay $2oa Riverpaw Gnolls and defeat Barkpaw.', 'Me apologies, matey! New to the bow! More of a sword arm, yeah?!\n\nDidn\'t mean ta give ya such a start! It\'s just that we\'re in a bit of a bind, me an\' the crew here!\n\nCan ya give us a bit of a hand?! Some upright dogs attacked us in the dead of night! Chased us out of camp in our skivvies!\n\nMaybe ya can help?! They had some sort of big one as their boss! We\'ve been callin\' him Barkpaw on account of he was barkin\' at us and had big ol\' paws!', '', '', '', '', '', '', 32978),
